  "Description": {
    "English": "Replaces the heat sink of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cyclotron Ballista</span> by encompassing the entire unit with a heat-absorbing megastructure. Heat output is recycled to boost combat efficiency.<br><br>Significantly improves <span class=\"name name-stellar\">heat performance</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用吸热巨型结构包围整个装置，取代<span class=\"name name-technology\">回旋加速弩炮</span>的散热器。回收热量输出以提升战斗效率。<br><br>显著提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">热性能</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "用吸热巨型结构包围整个装置，取代<span class=\"name name-technology\">回旋加速弩炮</span>的提示接收器。回收热量输出以提升战斗效率。<br><br>显著提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">热性能</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "用吸熱巨型結構包圍整個裝置，取代<span class=\"name name-technology\">迴旋加速弩砲</span>的散熱器。回收熱量輸出以提升戰鬥效率。<br><br>顯著提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">熱性能</span>。"
  },
